title: 6/6/17 - When our government betrays our protectors (Jay Dobyns Joins The Program)

Mike Broomhead in for Glenn Beck ...Fast & Furious hearing coming to Capitol Hill ...Latest updates on The London terrorist attack ... Bernie Sanders: Socialist or Capitalist?...Remember American heroes on this D-Day Anniversary ...How did document leaker Reality Winner get top secret clearance in the first place? ....Breaking news out of Paris ...The very latest out of London ...How does a 25 year old even get top secret clearance? ...Former ATF agent Jay Dobyns discusses the facts of Fast & Furious and why they matter ...The man who infiltrated the Hell's Angels ...When our government betrays our protectors ...Food stamp rates dropping in one US state.
